<br>
&quot;We hold these truths to be self-evident, that <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>   all</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> men are created equal, that they are <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>   endowed by their Creator</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> with certain unalienable Rights, that among these are Life, Liberty and the pursuit of Happiness.&quot;<br>
